Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%8Bch-phong/poem-oeXd7-PMf-mvXh8JPO9RUQ">Tịch phong - 夕烽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-KNX6BNCUyYmM6AxcK2Q5Pg">Tự đề - 自題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-kinh-ph%C3%AC-th%E1%BA%A3-di-c%C6%B0-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93n-mao-%E1%BB%91c-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-5rLUg3P0nmMevzZgjaqOLA">Tự Nhương Tây kinh phì thả di cư Đông Đồn mao ốc kỳ 1 - 自瀼西荊扉且移居東屯茅屋其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C3%A3n-thu-tham-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-8yN40zXtbKGw_HZ44xR_oQ">Vãn thu tham thiền - 晚秋參禪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
